General.Name: Sky Gold Limited
General.Description: Sky Gold Limited designs, assembles, cuts, polishes, manufactures, and sells gold and silver jewelry in India. The company offers rings, studs, necklaces, bracelets, lockers, chains, kadas, bangles, nose pins, and leg chains, as well as wedding and kids jewelry. It also imports, exports, buys, sells, deals, distributes, and wholesales jewelry. Sky Gold Limited was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Mumbai, India.
